description: Urban Waste Water treatment Directive  concerns  the collection, treatment and discharge of urban waste water and  the treatment and discharge of waste water from certain industrial sectors. The objective of the Directive is to protect the environment from the adverse effects of  the  above mentioned waste water discharges.
